init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana Knights have a special relationship with the Mana Goddess.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are the only ones who can hear her voice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is the one who gives them their power, and she is the one who decides who will be a Mana Knight.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mana Knights are able to use Mana to cast spells, which are called "Mana Arts".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These spells are based on the four elements of Earth, Fire, Wind and Water.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mana Knights are also able to use Mana to enhance their physical abilities, such as strength and speed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mana Knights can also use Mana to create magical weapons and armor.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These items are called "Mana Tools" and are the only weapons that can harm the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mana Knights are also able to create magical barriers, which are called "Mana Shields".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mana Knights are able to use Mana to heal themselves and others.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are also able to use Mana to create portals to other dimensions, and to travel through time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana Knights are led by the Mana Knight Commander, who is the strongest Mana Knight.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana Knights are also led by a council of elders, who are the strongest Mana Knights in each of the four elements.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Earth is the element of strength and power.
